level: A1
title: Imperative and Requests
word_target: 1200
content_outline:
- title: Наказовий спосіб (Imperative Mood)
  slug: imperative-mood-intro
  words: 300
  points:
  - Introduce the concept of giving commands and instructions using English scaffolding.
  - 'Explain the formation rule for the informal singular ''ти'' form: drop the ''-ти''
    ending from the infinitive.'
  - 'Explain the formal/plural ''ви'' form: add ''-те'' or ''-іть'' to the ''ти''
    command.'
  - Address the common error of confusing personal commands with general infinitive
    forms.
- title: Вісім обов'язкових дієслів (Eight Required Verbs)
  slug: eight-required-verbs
  words: 350
  points:
  - 'Introduce the 8 essential A1 verbs: читай(те), пиши(те), скажи(те), дай(те),
    іди(те), слухай(те), дивись(те), стій(те).'
  - Highlight the irregular stems that must be memorized as set phrases (дати → дай,
    сказати → скажи, стояти → стій).
  - Provide clear, short examples in classroom and daily contexts (e.g., Читайте текст,
    Слухайте уважно).
- title: Ввічливе прохання (Polite Requests)
  slug: polite-requests
  words: 250
  points:
  - Introduce 'будь ласка' (please) as the universal politeness marker to soften direct
    commands.
  - Demonstrate its flexible placement in a sentence (beginning, middle, or end).
  - Present 'Прошу вас' + infinitive for more formal, service-oriented situations.
- title: Заборони (Prohibitions)
  slug: prohibitions
  words: 150
  points:
  - Explain how to form negative commands by simply placing 'Не' before the imperative
    verb (e.g., Не біжи!, Не кури!).
  - Briefly note the difference between a personal spoken prohibition ('Не чіпай!')
    and a public sign prohibition ('Не торкатися!').
- title: Практика і підсумок (Summary and Practice)
  slug: summary-and-practice
  words: 150
  points:
  - Recap the 'ти' vs 'ви' endings and the critical role of 'будь ласка'.
  - 'Self-check 1: How do you change a ''ти'' command to a ''ви'' command?'
  - 'Self-check 2: What are the imperative forms of the irregular verbs ''дати'' and
    ''сказати''?'
  - 'Self-check 3: How do you make a command negative?'
